## Model Training

::: {#cf9d1920 .cell execution_count=5}
``` {.python .cell-code}
rf = RandomForestClassifier(
    n_estimators=400,
    max_features="sqrt",
    min_samples_leaf=2,
    random_state=42,
    n_jobs=-1
)
rf.fit(X_train, y_train)
```

